    "205494246": {
      "title": "ATR: an essential regulator of genome integrity",
      "abstract": "ATR kinase and the related ATM kinase have overlapping but non-redundant functions in the DNA-damage response that maintains genome integrity. ATR signals to regulate DNA replication, cell-cycle transitions and DNA repair through the phosphorylation of various substrates."
